                              PREAMBLE
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

The Shadow Public License (SPL) is a specialized license designed for 
cybersecurity tools and penetration testing software. This license aims to:

  • Promote responsible use of security testing tools
  • Protect the author from liability for misuse
  • Encourage collaboration within the security community
  • Ensure ethical usage in authorized contexts only

This license is specifically crafted for "ShadowScan" and related security 
tools developed by Mahara HOSEN SIAM.

